showerReviews.reviewText:
Unfortunately a lot of minus for room 6 namely:
No hot water;
The shower head dirty and lots of limoscale;
The shower cabin floor extra slippery;
The room ceiling and walls full of cracks;
I share the room with a bugs family;
Windows dirty and water track  between double glaze unit;
Car park min. 7 min away.
Unfortunately this location its a total disappointment due to the big potential!

